#!/bin/bash&#10;projectRoot=&quot;/home/projects/solanahacker&quot;&#10;journalDir=&quot;$projectRoot/memory/journal&quot;&#10;&#10;now=$(date -d &apos;7 days ago&apos; +%Y-%m-%d)&#10;echo &quot;Journal cleanup dry-run (older than $now):&quot;&#10;deleted=0&#10;&#10;for file in &quot;$journalDir&quot;/*.md; do&#10;  basename_file=$(basename &quot;$file&quot;)&#10;  if [[ $basename_file =~ ^([0-9]{4}-[0-9]{2}-[0-9]{2})\.md$ ]]; then&#10;    date_str=${BASH_REMATCH[1]}&#10;    if [[ $date_str &lt; $now ]]; then&#10;      echo &quot;Would delete: $basename_file ($date_str)&quot;&#10;      ((deleted++))&#10;    fi&#10;  fi&#10;done&#10;&#10;echo &quot;Dry-run complete. Would delete $deleted files.&quot;